            <paragraph>这个 <strong>OccluderInstance3D</strong> 的遮挡器资源。要生成遮挡器资源，你可以先选中 <strong>OccluderInstance3D</strong> 节点，然后使用编辑器顶部的<strong>烘焙遮挡器</strong>按钮。</paragraph>
            <paragraph>你还可以通过在“检查器”中为 <reference internal="True" refid="class-occluderinstance3d-property-occluder"><inline classes="std std-ref">occluder</inline></reference> 属性添加新的 <reference internal="True" refuri="class_polygonoccluder3d#class-polygonoccluder3d"><inline classes="std std-ref">PolygonOccluder3D</inline></reference> 资源来绘制自己的 2D 遮挡器多边形。</paragraph>
            <paragraph>另外，你也可以选择要使用的基本遮挡器：<reference internal="True" refuri="class_quadoccluder3d#class-quadoccluder3d"><inline classes="std std-ref">QuadOccluder3D</inline></reference>、<reference internal="True" refuri="class_boxoccluder3d#class-boxoccluder3d"><inline classes="std std-ref">BoxOccluder3D</inline></reference>、<reference internal="True" refuri="class_sphereoccluder3d#class-sphereoccluder3d"><inline classes="std std-ref">SphereOccluder3D</inline></reference>。</paragraph>
